{"tid":2325000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓74歲老翁因追求30來歲女士不成 竟直接拿出鹽酸潑人","createTime":"2020-12-14T10:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T11:50:49.000Z","uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8445c493f4cbe07138a2e3cff5fd8542059b13ec","tid":2325000,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"老牛吃嫩草吃不到，竟然惱羞成怒！南韓1名74歲的老翁，因為追求30來歲輕熟女不成，竟在餐廳裡拿出鹽酸潑人，雖然女方驚險逃過一劫，但現場的顧客和員工遭到波及。<br />\n<br />\n據《韓聯社》報導，該名老翁12日前往南韓首爾市道峰區的一家餐館等候，輕熟女則於晚間6時30分許赴約，期間老翁竟拿出鹽酸潑灑，結果反而沾到自己的臉龐，還濺到1名顧客和1名員工的手腳。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，老翁這幾個月一直苦苦追求女方，希望能夠和她交往，道峰警察局在申請逮捕令後，於今天（14日）將老翁逮捕歸案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3380878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3380878&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=e26b2f48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3380878&h=98f00f50\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3380878</a>"},{"pid":"d2c4cd9cb6d3a37b82a2853b36ee7e5cd71b9440","tid":2325000,"uid":8482,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46442fc0c03ecc5edede30895bee6f8c9111033d","tid":2325000,"uid":83251,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"韓國不意外"},{"pid":"9d550dc41a598b6c91e17e17d90080907e034399","tid":2325000,"uid":190579,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d2c4cd9cb6d3a37b82a2853b36ee7e5cd71b9440","tid":2325000,"uid":8482,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-1